EFMesh Ambassador Firmware
==========================

This repository contains customizations layered on top of the upstream
Meshtastic firmware ambassador module.

Upstream
--------

  Original ambassador module + documentation:
    https://github.com/ascendr/meshtastic/tree/main/ambassador
  Original firmware source (ambassador branch of a Meshtastic fork):
    https://github.com/ascendr/firmware/tree/ambassador
  Upstream Meshtastic firmware:
    https://github.com/meshtastic/firmware

  Original AmbassadorModule.cpp / AmbassadorModule.h and the supporting
  NodeDB.cpp / Modules.cpp hooks were written by Tony "ascendr" and
  released under the GNU General Public License v3.0, the same license
  as upstream Meshtastic firmware.

