EFMesh modifications
--------------------

  The Electric Forest Meshtastic Community (EFMesh, https://efmesh.com)
  modifications are limited to three places:

    1. CannedMessageModule.cpp — default ambassador invite text.
    2. userPrefs.jsonc — default owner long_name and short_name.

